posts.subject: Anon Collaboration Index
posts.body:
Isn't this place built better for collaborations compared to other chans on the clearnet? There should be artistic anons working with others, seeing as you can upload your work directly with next to no limitations. 

With that being said, what would you like to collaborate on? Do you have any ideas to share? Any anons interested in starting a project.

Ok. Guess that's a start.

I write, compose music and want to get into drawing and animation (although the last two I currently suck at). Would be good to have a skill learning thread of sorts. Just need to be bothered to do it first.
